TEST create_user_already_exists

RECEIVE HTTP:POST /api/v1/users
WITH {{payloads/create_user_request.json}}

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT * FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`email` = 'john@example.com' LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS {{payloads/user_response.json}}

RESPOND HTTP:409
WITH {{payloads/user_exists_error.json}}
